data.description: South Georgia Homes presents the Faye plan- a 2119 SQ FT ranch with 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms.  Past the foyer and side staircase, you enter the open concept living space of the Faye plan.  The kitchen, with large center island and granite counter tops, opens into the breakfast room and over sized great room.  The great room has a shiplap surround fireplace as the focal point of the room.  Off the great room is a large covered patio enjoy the warm summer evenings.  Upstairs is the bright and airy master bedroom.  The master bath has a double sink vanity with granite counter tops, shower, garden tub and built in shelving for extra storage.  The laundry room is upstairs, conveniently across from the master bedroom.  There are 3 additional bedrooms upstairs that share a bathroom.  This home comes with a fully landscaped yard.  Greenpoint is Harlem's 1st master planned community with streetlights, sidewalks, and green space parks for the residents to enjoy!
